creator: HR Tech
descriptionHtml:
This course will provide exposure to basic biology and engineering problems associated with living systems and health care delivery. Examples will be used to illustrate how basic concepts and tools of science and engineering can be brought to bear in understanding, mimicking, and utilizing biological processes. The course will focus on four areas: biotechnology, biomechanics, biomaterials, and tissue engineering. The course will also cover bioimaging and will introduce the basic life sciences and engineering concepts associated with these topics.



Topics covers in this app are as follows

Amplifiers
Learn Artificial Neural Network
Learn Analog Communication
Learn Antenna Theory
Learn Automata Theory
Learn Basic Electronics
Learn Biometrics
Communication Technologies
Control Systems
Convex Optimization
